These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, pepper, potato
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, tea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, scientific
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, surfing
1. the person eating pepper is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's sport is baseball##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Food          | corn      | pepper        | potato     |
| Beverage         | tea | iced-tea | almond-milk    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | musical       | scientific |
| Sport         | baseball  | climbing      | surfing    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, egyptian, indian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, thriller
3 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the egyptian##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the egyptian is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the indian##3
6. the indian is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person watching disaster movies and the spanish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Nationality           | egyptian    | indian | spanish |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action       | thriller   |
| Pet           | hamster  | guinea-pig   | ferret     |
| Sport         | lacrosse | tennis       | baseball   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cranberry, watermelon
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, adventure, family
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, turtle
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, trance, metal
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the fan of metal##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the person eating carrot is between the person watching adventure movies and the fan of metal##2
5. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the turtle is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | carrot | cranberry |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | action | adventure |
| Pet           | pony       | bird   | turtle    |
| Music-Genre     | metal      | rock   | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, photography, woodworking
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, engineer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, cain, chaman
There are 3 different nationalities: british, italian, pakistani
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
2. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the engineer is the cain-smoker##1
4. the italian is on the far right##1
5. the bartender is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the italian is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Hobby         | photography  | chess       | woodworking |
| Job           | engineer     | doctor      | bartender   |
| Cigar   | cain | siglo | chaman     |
| Nationality   | british      | pakistani   | italian     |

