.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, cauliflower, raspberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, photographer, social-worker
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, may, february
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the photographer and the person eating cauliflower##2
2. the person who's birthday is in january is the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person watching western movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the social-worker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Food          | raspberry    | asparagus     | cauliflower |
| Job           | photographer | social-worker | doctor      |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | mystery       | disaster    |
| Birthday   | may      | january         | february     |

