The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, photographer, police-officer
There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, turkish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, rowing
1. the american is the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the dancer##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the police-officer and the person traveling to nizza##2
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| City         | liverpool    | hamburg   | nizza      |
| Job           | police-officer | dancer    | photographer |
| Nationality   | american       | argentine | turkish      |
| Sport         | rowing         | parkour   | climbing     |

