.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-16::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, peas, tomato
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, epic, family
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, soccer, weightlifting
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, jet-ski
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Food          | peas     | pear   | tomato     |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | epic   | drama      |
| Sport   | soccer | golf | weightlifting    |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | boat   | helicopter |

